# Research rig (offline analysis + cached FMP data) — not imported by the app.
# Keeping it out of deploys avoids a multi-GB upload of research/data/cache.
#
# LEADING SLASH IS LOAD-BEARING. Unanchored `research/` matches a directory of that
# name at ANY depth, which silently excluded `lib/research/` from every deploy — so
# the research contract modules were not merely uncalled, they were undeployable.
# The first commit to `require()` one of them 500'd /api/tracker?op=today in prod.
# Anchor every directory rule here unless you genuinely mean "at any depth".
/research/

# Offline Python screener pipeline (CSV triage tool) — not imported by the app.
/tools/

# logs & local cruft
*.log
.DS_Store
/scratchpad/
